<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA7">
<l>yāṉē tavamuṭaiyē ṉeṉṉeñcē naṉṉeñcam</l>
<l>yāṉē piṟappaṟuppā ṉeṇṇiṉēṉ - yāṉēyak</l>
<l>kaimmā vuripōrtta kaṇṇutalāṉ veṇṇīṟṟa</l>
<l>vammāṉuk kāḷāyi ṉēṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I, I possess penance, my heart. Good heart,</l>
<l>I, I count on cutting off birth. I,</l>
<l>I have become the servant of the lord [smeared] with white ash,</l>
<l>him with a forehead eye, wrapped in the hide of that trunk-animal.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
